{"tid":276957,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"周綺萍批實習生隨時令公司有所損失  實習制度企業認真付出","createTime":"2017-06-09T08:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T11:26:46.000Z","uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0345bae4284d2a402c0a3455dcc9e8436882f55","tid":276957,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:27:17.000Z","msg":"周綺萍：若學生實習計較人工　就不應拿取學分<br />\n<br />\n安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍接受《香港01》訪問時表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">實習制度企業認真付出，實習生亦未必會留在企業工作回報公司，隨時令公司有所損失。至於有學生認為「學嘢」並非實習低薪或無薪的藉口。周認為實習就是為了「學到嘢」，如有學生對報酬感到不甘，亦不應拿取相關學分。</span>「最終目的都唔同，你覺得人工唔夠嘅，咁你都唔應該拎取學分」認為實習的最終目的與「手板眼見功夫」的兼職、暑期工不同，前者為幫助日後就職，而後者是為金錢報酬。周亦表示，自己以往於銀行實習，亦沒任何薪金。"},{"pid":"3f1e3a02c3d8dca7a92f97cb34d2906943785823","tid":276957,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1474a68f27c683127d2b3300a1bb0bf06e4410d7","tid":276957,"uid":40146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"遲d連學徒都唔應該出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381f6a8dc2f10d48d35ad1f2f7e0471dd35dba1f","tid":276957,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075dcb949d2b5667d5973ebd5c759b395d54f469","tid":276957,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"又係周小姐呢條臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166608f9c69b10405766a51565eb39f1d4391a99","tid":276957,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"周小姐以前食開屎而家要迫我地食屎"},{"pid":"b42a5bd18da00a0508cec450807c774c16056a9c","tid":276957,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"好彩jp morgan 無請你，人地d大行為左搶叻學生，